Package: birdseyeview
Type: Package
Title: Make Planning Maps, Tables, and Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eli Pousson <eli.pousson@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Eli Pousson <eli.pousson@gmail.com>
Description: This package helps create maps, tables, and figures for planning documents using open spatial data. 
    birdseyeview is designed to work with the overedge package and relies on sf, ggplot2, and gt.
